	<conbody>
		<section id="contentref_attribute_term">
			
			<p>When a topic references a complete topic or smaller piece of content with the &lt;conref&gt; attribute, the referenced content gets dynamically copied into the referencing topic. If the referenced topic is changed and the document containing the referencing topic is rebuilt, the new version of the referenced topic is automatically replaced.</p>
		</section>
